Class RGBColour

  • java.lang.Object
    • facilitators.RGBColour
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class RGBColour
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents a Colour in form of the RGB Code. Every shape has a Colour which consists out of RGBColour and opacity.
    See Also:
    Shape, Colour, Serialized Form
